headline: Cineverse Adds Three Industry Veterans to Accelerate Feature Film Acquisitions and Releasing Business
summary: Cineverse (Nasdaq: CNVS), a next-generation entertainment studio, has announced today the addition of three development, acquisitions and distributions experts to the recently-formed Cineverse Motion Pictures Group led by Chief Motion Pictures Officer Yolanda Macias.
